%3Fv%3DYZEE-nM2iNE&d=beIwg85N8Ddzcl6rIyS0GTIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=f5aaf9fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=YZEE-nM2iNE</a><br />\n<br />\n【十月行動討論】抵制十一，歡慶雙十，全民贈慶！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581858</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我地應該盡可能團結所有可以團結嘅人，要向大陸輸出革命，同時連結台灣<span style=\"color: gold;\">大家可以喺連儂牆上貼滿慶祝中華民國國慶嘅宣傳單張，順便貼下中共呢70年犯下嘅種種歷史罪行，去到10月10號呢一日我地應該要大肆慶祝中華民國國慶</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1dEhxUj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1dEhxUj.jpg&h=738a6b69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家留意下共匪版本仲要係遮住「青天白日滿地紅旗」（即係中華民國國旗）剩係show 民進黨旗，<span style=\"color: red;\">可見共匪係好驚中華民國國旗公諸於大陸人面前，共匪更加驚大陸人知道中華民國先係正統中國而共匪本身只係一個簒國政權</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">10月10號呢一日我地應該要大肆慶祝中華民國國慶</span></span>"},{"pid":"2d6cd306282bbdc2a047b87c997f8ec2742bee02","tid":1617704,"uid":226126,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:26:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e579abc4cca17539cd1bd5d4a178864699f5e2de","tid":1617704,"uid":49563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d6cd306282bbdc2a047b87c997f8ec2742bee02","tid":1617704,"uid":226126,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a46a4854ee3c3b90cabc5eeba63bf5a0d8b600df","tid":1617704,"uid":280681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:22:13.000Z","msg":"今日1個鐘車程得10個有戴<br />\n今日冇戴既 唔該放工放學買返個<br />\n聽日繼續戴"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:26:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:51:02.000Z","msg":"你估連仔係毅進仔<br />\n咁容易心靈受創<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bc46676b9e09a9b798627cad9ff131f159979d1","tid":1617704,"uid":4559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:53:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}